name: Taalmu alleyways
description:
Navigating through the mazelike alleys of Taalmu can be challenging.
Try not to get lost or worse.

paths.taalmu: Getting back on the main street is easy as it.
paths.taalmu_market: Sounds of people bartering and talking leads to the market.
paths.taalmu_port: The smell of salt leads the way to the port.
paths.taalmu_black_market: You can see a shady part of Taalmu further down an alleyway.
